User: riccardo  Fri Sep 20 01:50:19 PDT 2002
HepRepSvc

Log Message:
First release of HepRepSvc package; this package provides methods to produce HepRep representations of
an actual event in the TDS and of the GLAST geometry. Various concrete representation can be supported; this
version support XML persistency file production, while a CORBA representation will be provided by another
package. This release is for test purpouses and will likely rapidly change in the near future.


Status:

Vendor Tag:	GLAST
Release Tags:	v0r1
		
